{"tid":2067724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林肯雕像都有人請願話要拆","createTime":"2020-06-17T07:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T11:46:01.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e3b304d1055a8f39accea5fc91eff0c79e9c1a","tid":2067724,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"綜合外媒報導，波士頓公園廣場一座百年歷史的「林肯解放紀念雕像」，成為黑人平權運動的眼中釘之一，因為該雕像的形象為林肯以站立姿態，俯視一名跪在他腳邊，手上鐵鍊遭破除的非裔男子，上頭寫著「獲得自由的種族與國家和平，林肯從中得到了安息。」<br />\n<br />\n移除雕像的請願書上寫道，「我自小就看著這座雕像，這應該象徵著自由，但凸顯的卻是我們仍受到他人的壓迫。」&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n位於首府華盛頓的國會山莊也有一座相同的林肯解放雕像，同樣引起當地居民的不悅，希望能夠撤除，有民眾說，「這座雕像讓我感到失去尊重，好像黑人就是低人一等。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3200286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3200286&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=14900598\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3200286&h=9f7ac322\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3200286</a>"},{"pid":"071c60ec314c6989ad1117cab8659f4d7f8ad2c5","tid":2067724,"uid":225798,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"中共文化大革命"},{"pid":"1fa008842e4f838fac1cd522ff4cf85ea8711db2","tid":2067724,"uid":14494,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"馬丁路德金幾時會比人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d1be2c1a65249fe13e773050a4203520ee3d79","tid":2067724,"uid":162095,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"班nigga有咩咁慘<br />\n而家拎晒光環啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla